  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      D.fragilis is an intestinal protozoon that feeds by phagocytosis of intestinal bacteria. The
      study aim to determine if the carriage of the intestinal parasite D.fragilis is associated to
      changes of gut microbiota in subjects presenting with or without intestinal symptoms.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
